name: Say My Name Bracelet
description:
One personalized bracelet turned into a huge demand for more! So here you have it, our custom Say My Name bracelet. 

Choose from a selection of 5 beautiful fonts and 6 super cute optional design endings. All our bracelets are individually handcrafted in brass and then gold plated. The total length is 7.1 inches which is standard for women. If you need a different length please email us after ordering with one of the following measurements: 5.1 / 5.9 / 6.7 / 7.1 / 7.5 / 8.3 / 9 inches
Nameplates are slighted curved to wrap perfectly around wrists.

*If the name you want is more than 7 lowercases, 5 uppercases or 1 uppercase with 6 lowercases, please email us first at info@soprettylike.com for a quote with a slightly higher price. 


PLEASE FOLLOW THESE INSTRUCTIONS WHEN PLACING AN ORDER:

1. Write the name/word exactly as you want it written.

2. Write the font you want. 

3. Pick a design to go at the end of your name(optional).

3. After purchasing, immediately send an email to info@soprettylike.com with the details for your bracelet like this:

"Nija" in the font #2 and the bow design.
